# Design system

Read `docs/design-system.md` before changing UI.

## Non-negotiables
- Use CSS variables from `css/style.css` — never hardcode colors in components.
- kebab-case class names; state via `.active` or `.is-*`.
- Inline SVG icons with `currentColor` (16px header, ~48px hub tiles).
- Reuse `.btn`, `.btn-icon`, `.dialog`, surface+border patterns before inventing new components.

## Hub
- 3×3 grid: `.hub-grid`, `.hub-tile`, `.hub-tile--soon` for unavailable games.
- Tiles extend button surface language (border, radius, hover).

## Key files
- `css/style.css`, `css/mahjong.css`, `index.html`, `js/hub.js`
